data.description: This neat 3-story home in Banning Lewis Ranch should absolutely be at the top of your list! Come into this well-kept home at the main floor, which offers a spacious living room, with a huge island and a stunning kitchen, with the most beautiful countertops. A large patio extends from the walkout kitchen, overlooking the large backyard. A master's bedroom with attached master bath is also located on the main level, as well as an additional half bath for guests. The second level opens into a small loft perfect for seating and provides 2 spacious bedrooms with tons of closet space. An additional full bath is also located on the second level. The basement is the perfect place for entertaining guests or just wanting a second family room. Garage access is also located in the basement, as are the laundry accommodations, not taking anything away from the oversized room. The zero-scaped backyard hosts several flower beds throughout and the gorgeous central firepit offers an overlook of Pikes Peak. It makes those crisp fall Colorado days even more enjoyable. The community center has incredible amenities, perfect for every lifestyle. This home sits less than a block from the neighborhood park and open space. Tons of biking and strolling paths are strategically located throughout the sprawling Banning Lewis community. 20ish minutes from Peterson SFB and 35ish minutes to Fort Carson and Schriever SFB.
